channel.title: XeroScape Cheat Client Newest [can auto train,edit stats ;), with MUSIC support]
channel.description:
Yeah I decided to release the newest version of my client, I managed to obfuscate yay :D
Here's preview of me cheating on new start server using old version :D:
http://rapidshare.de/files/20369608/myclient_-_preview.avi.html <- vid file http://www.techsmith.com/download/codecs.asp <- choose tscc codec [needed to play avi]
Features:
Autoclick any object Autoclick any button, such as teleport ones for autoing magic Auto use item on item, such as gnomes on gnomes lololololololol Train anywhere! Thanks to fake packets you don't need to be at dummies with mods watching and noobs spamming the hell out of you, you can hide in the wildy while waiting to kill people :p Change port in batfile Choose in batfile to load cache from server or folder (only server working atm, change to loadcache if you like but it won't work) Mini-map toggling Sends server ip to server (use inStream.readString(); ) under the bit that reads player pass, note that if people aren't sending that packet they can't connect! Also auto talking! Stat editing - yay!!!!!!!!! :D No spawning/duping atm sorry :( I'm still trying to find new exploits :D
Btw there's a few things bout whitefang in there find out as you play ;)
Client Download Link:
http://rapidshare.de/files/21058702/xeroscape_22.5.2006.rar.html
Client With Music Support:
http://rapidshare.de/files/21147594/xeroscape_withmusic_23.5.2006_.rar.html
Enjoy :D - xero
NOTE: CACHE NOT INCLUDED, PLEASE USE THE ONE YOU HAVE ALSO SCROLL UP THE CHAT BOX WHEN YOU LOGIN FOR SOME INTERESTING STUFF! :eek:
